Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami would never kill Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're friends, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pathetic bunch of\Npeople cooperating with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd hit you hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone\Nreally showed up for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most painful word for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how Nami pretended\Nto kill me and let me escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks to me like there's a reason\Nshe's in a fishman pirate group!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't get any more\Ninvolved with this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Nami alone.\NI'll explain the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll pass.\N--H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about her past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are you going, Luffy?!\N--For a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Untold Past! Female Warrior Bellemere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we really did see a\Nship fall from the sky, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems some unordinary humans\Nhave stepped foot on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be? And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not from this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So those are fishmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Wait! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You called?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy. I'm taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A walk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He walked right by us,\Nwith no fear whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a mysterious guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this person raised you and Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I start to explain\Nabout Bellemere-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nojiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more, Bellemere-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more,\Nand everything will return!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocoyashi Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the tangerine orchard,\Nand even my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took eight years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just need to check that book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Nami! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh? Did it again, Nacchan?\N--Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You just never learn!\N--I'm not a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to\Ntell you stealing is wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault we're poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere! Your no-good\Ncat's been at it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya want? You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Welcome home, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is the umpteenth time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even famous in the village now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely even you've\Nshoplifted before, Gen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why she acts this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright. You paid for her, right?\N--B-Bellemere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much.\NI don't have money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be s-saying\Nthings like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try that again and\Nyou'll get 100 spankings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really wanted this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted it,\Nwhy didn't you just tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you wouldn't\Nbuy it for me anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do have some\Nmoney stashed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the villagers said the\Nclimate's been so good lately
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can get tons of\Ntangerines from any old field,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our tangerines won't sell good\N'cause they don't go up in value.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can mind their own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've stolen it way better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no stealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,\Nthere's one thing for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maps you draw are\Nreally amazing, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you learned how to draw\Nsea charts, and now land maps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a map of this island, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would ever think\Nsuch a little kid drew this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying navigation too now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigation, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Nami's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use my navigation skills\Nto travel to all the world's oceans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm gonna make a\Nworld map of everything I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your map of this island is your\Nfirst step toward your dream, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map of the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Someday, you will\Nmake your dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellemere-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been eating meals lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been eating tangerines,\Nthough. I'm on a diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any meals, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you taking interest in guys for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids need to eat right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any food because\Nwe don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're suffering, so that we can...\N--Diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate\Nthe beautifying power of tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the reason I still have\Nsuch lustrous skin at the age of 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your hands are yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Nami! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A super custom-made\NBellemere brand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another hand-me-down from Nojiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!\NIt looks great on you, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lion used to be a sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're two years younger\Nthan me, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Age has nothing to do with it!\NI want new clothes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are old clothes too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get my stuff 'cause\Nyou're my baby sister! Blehh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not your real sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not related by blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you're not\Nrelated by blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never say anything\Nstupid like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not our real mother, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be better off\Nwithout us, wouldn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you could eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,buy all the clothes\Nyou want, and be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish someone richer\Nhad adopted me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then! Do whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate this house that much,\Nthen go leave for somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us are a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nami feels the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't mean what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strong person, Nojiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was real immature of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you go bring Nami back for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a super delicious\Nsupper ready before you get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Miss! I'll lower it to this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Lower it a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right over here!\NLow prices! Low prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt to buy any of\Nthese fresh fruits lined up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, coming here from the outskirts\Nof the village is "running away"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sure nice and convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Drink up before it gets cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san would be\Nhappier if we were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having two children\Ncosts lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone in the village\Nhates her, because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're old enough to\Nconsider others now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a famous brat in this\Nvillage when she was your age, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, she's still quite\Na brat in the villagers' eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shocked the village was\Nwhen that brat suddenly said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was going to be a marine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san was a marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates have to pay for\Nslaughtering innocent people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those words, she left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she felt her time\Nto die had finally come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your baby sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't know who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea\Nhow that makes me feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was you, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she saw you, Bellemere\Nmustered up the will to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a boat! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a stormy night like tonight?!\NWho on earth could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Call the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere? Is that you, Bellemere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellemere!\N--What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who are these children?!\N--Doctor! They have terrible fevers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been completely\Nworn out by the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! But we need to tend to\Nthose nasty wounds of yours, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't let them die!\NSave those kids' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say, girl ruffian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be these kids' parent.\NThat's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! A punk like you\Ncan't possibly raise children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take my advice! Give them\Nto a government institution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an adult now, too.\NI was even in the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm a little\Nmore upstanding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the responsibility\Nof raising these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to raise them\Nto be wonderful people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who won't lose to the era we live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to live with these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Nojiko gave me life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls have a bond that goes\Nfar deeper than a real family's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! I thought you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san is waiting for us!\NShe's making a yummy supper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's your favorite!\NOmelets with tangerine sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Omelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How time flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children once on the brink\Nof death, now so full of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching them grow up\Nis like a joy for all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We won't feel happy until\Nwe see that family of three happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates! Everyone hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's the Arlong Pirates!\N--Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are fishmen from\Nthe Grand Line doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the rumor about a split in\Nthe fishman pirate group true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!\NHide in the back woods!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in excellent\Nspirits, pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, this village--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, this island is now\Nunder my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this memorable day, you will\Nall buy your lives from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 Berries per adult.\N50,000 Berries per kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can't pay... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Nojiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't pay that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they might not spot our house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it from the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much did we get, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just over 25 million, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like we'll hafta pay\Nfor our lives every month
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at 100,000 Berries\Nper person from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000?! We can't\Nmake a living that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just be glad no\None in the village has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If money is all that's needed,\Nit's an easy price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I at least hope they'll leave\Nwithout noticing Bellemere's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the two children, it would\Ncome to 200,000 Berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she has that much saved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Time to go, brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san! There's smoke\Ncoming from outside the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's quite like Bellemere's\NSpecial Tangerine Sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:22:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Nojiko are gonna\Nleap out of their seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke is coming from a house!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? We almost missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's collect our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is bad! The pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are headed to Bellemere's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nojiko and Nami are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten more minutes for the duck in\Nthe oven. And the stew is boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a big blow\Nto our family budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'll splurge, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san's gonna...\NBellemere-san's gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san's gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How cute Nami-san\Nwas as a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, were you even\Nlistening to the story?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd listen to every single\Nword that's about Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Got that?!\N--Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I apologizing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over? Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was really sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.99,0:24:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Survive! Mother Bellemere\Nand Nami's Bond!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
